name: Duality - VPN & Proxy
summary:
Duality VPN gives you fast, secure, and private internet access — free to start. Protect your data, browse safely on public Wi-Fi, and enjoy smooth connections wherever you are.

Duality VPN lets you exclude VPN traffic within your own country, so you get the fastest local speeds whilst still benefiting from VPN protection for other connections. Choose from a wide selection of global server locations, all designed for reliable and private browsing.
